title: Chris.Ryans.Elite.World.Cops.S01E05.Israel.PDTV.XviD
description:
The author and former SAS soldier shadows the world's most remarkable police units as they confront crime on the frontline. In Israel, Ryan faces his most difficult task yet as he joins the Magav, the country's border security force which has to police arguably the most disputed territorial boundary in the world. Aside from the political dimension of dealing with their Palestinian neighbours, the Magav also have to counter a range of criminal activities such as drug dealing.
